Package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1

Package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1 is a program for computing a matrix product using M2MI with omnihandles.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Matrix Interface Matrix specifies the interface for an exported M2MI object that encapsulates a matrix.
Worker Interface Worker specifies the interface for an exported M2MI object that computes one element in the product of two matrices.
 

Class Summary
MatrixImpl Class MatrixImpl provides an exported M2MI object that encapsulates a matrix.
MatrixProduct1 Class MatrixProduct1 is a main program that computes the product of two random matrices using M2MI.
WorkerImpl Class WorkerImpl encapsulates an exported M2MI object that computes one element in the product of two matrices.
 

Package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1 Description

Package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1 is a program for computing a matrix product using M2MI with omnihandles. Class MatrixProduct1 is the main program.

M2MI Library Version 02-Jul-2002
